h1. Adobe Experience Manager OSGI config (AEM) API Swagger AEM OSGI is an OpenAPI specification for Adobe Experience Manager (AEM) OSGI Configurations API

*Version:* 1.0.0-pre.0

----

{toc:printable=true|style=square|minLevel=2|maxLevel=3|type=list|outline=false|include=.*}
